---
title: Cranberry Apple Pork Chops with Roasted Baby Carrots and Herbed Potatoes
description: Apples, cranberries, baby carrots, potatoes, onion, and parsley: that’s not a shopping list for your next trip to the produce market. It’s all the fruit and veg bounty that’s in this recipe. So you can rest assured that your family will get their fill of their five-a-day with this dinner, plus a hearty serving of protein from the succulent, sauce-drizzled pork chops.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cranberry-apple-pork-chops-4431130a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/cranberry-apple-pork-chops-5c798d55e3f33922084679c2-9884bf8c.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/cranberry-apple-pork-chops-5c798d55e3f33922084679c2
cuisine: North America
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
time required: 40 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 700 kcal
